metadata.name: Exhausted
metadata.description:
She was taking a sun bath, rolling around on the moss.
She gave birth not too long ago, she must be exhausted.
Spring in Canada can be crazy, snow one day and 20+ degC the next. This was a beautiful afternoon after a very cold night.
All living creatures were so happy to be out!
Life is good my friends!
